ge un'inclinazione pi\u00f9 naturalistica, di derivazione leonardesca."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2408409", "itemLabel": "Cristoforo Solari", "dhsid": "018328", "namefr": "Cristoforo Solari", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristoforo_Solari", "namede": "", "articlede": "", "nameit": "Cristoforo Solari", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristoforo_Solari", "nameen": "Cristoforo Solari", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristoforo_Solari", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "133966569"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2408409", "wikipedia_page_title": "Cristoforo Solari", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "S", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/018328/2013-10-14"}